<paragraph id="29728DA6F6C90B1DAD7F5B3B9E789DC7" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
See 
<bibRefCitation id="AA16D4649D062324008BDB21E281D7B7" DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.147.2.1" author="Ariyawansa, HA" journalOrPublisher="Phytotaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="35 - 47" refId="B2" refString="Ariyawansa, HA, Kang, JC, Alias, SA, Chukeatirote, E, Hyde, KD, 2013. Towards a natural classification of Dothideomycetes: The genera Dermatodothella, Dothideopsella, Grandigallia, Hysteropeltella and Gloeodiscus (Dothideomycetesincertae sedis). . Phytotaxa 147: 35 - 47" title="Towards a natural classification of Dothideomycetes: The genera Dermatodothella, Dothideopsella, Grandigallia, Hysteropeltella and Gloeodiscus (Dothideomycetesincertae sedis)." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.147.2.1" volume="147" year="2013">Ariyawansa et al. (2013)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
